            {
               "text": "<h3>Minas Gerais - Brazil</h3>The image in this section shows the current territory of Minas Gerais, in Brazil (<i>Pindorama</i>). The state has had this shape since approximately the end of the colonial period. The word \"Pindorama\", meaning \"Land of the Palm Trees\", was the name used to refer to the region before the arrival of colonizers",
